  "texts": [
    "\"Impact of 3D Advertising on Product Knowledge, Brand Attitude, and Purchase Intention: The Mediating Role of Presence\", by Li et al. (2002), with six citations.",
    "They have explored the properties of 3D advertising and their impact on consumers, focusing on the sense of presence.",
    "In addition, to validate their theory, they have carried out two tests through different focus groups.",
    "\"Metaverse\", by Mystakidis (2022), with six citations.",
    "This paper holds forth the crucial parts of the Metaverse -immersive technologies -to propose their applicability in education."
  ]
}